title: Man In Manual Wheelchair Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a man using a manual wheelchair, with a medium-dark skin tone. It signifies mobility, accessibility, and independence.
apple_vendor_description: The man in a manual wheelchair emoji with a medium-dark skin tone, as designed on Apple devices, is depicted with dignity and mobility. The wheelchair itself is rendered with smooth, metallic sheen and realistic lighting, emphasizing its functional design. This emoji on Apple devices promotes inclusivity and represents individuals who use wheelchairs, conveying themes of independence and accessibility.
